In a bowl, combine all ingredients for the dressing and mix until smooth. Refrigerate. Cook peas, uncovered, in a large quantity of boiling water until al dente, about 5 minutes. Strain and refresh under cold water. In a bowl, toss cooled peas with feta and radishes. Add creamy dressing and toss gently. Serve topped with alfalfa sprouts and garnished with radish slices.